<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Trattoria Bella — Authentic Italian Cuisine</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0
        }

        :root {
            --cream: #F5F0E8;
            --warm-white: #FAF7F2;
            --gold: #B8860B;
            --gold-light: #D4A820;
            --brown: #3D2B1F;
            --brown-mid: #6B4226;
            --red: #8B1A1A;
            --text: #2A1F17;
            --text-muted: #7A6558;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Jost',sans-serif;
            background: var(--warm-white);
            color: var(--text);
            overflow-x: hidden
        }

        /* NAV */
        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1.5rem 4rem;
            background: rgba(250,247,242,0.92);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(184,134,11,0.2)
        }

        .nav-logo {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--brown);
            letter-spacing: .04em
        }

            .nav-logo span {
                color: var(--gold)
            }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2.5rem;
            list-style: none
        }

            .nav-links a {
                font-size: .78rem;
                letter-spacing: .14em;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                color: var(--text-muted);
                text-decoration: none;
                transition: color .2s
            }

                .nav-links a:hover {
                    color: var(--gold)
                }

        .nav-login {
            font-size: .75rem;
            letter-spacing: .12em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border: 1px solid var(--gold);
            color: var(--gold);
            padding: .55rem 1.4rem;
            background: transparent;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Jost',sans-serif;
            transition: all .25s
        }

            .nav-login:hover {
                background: var(--gold);
                color: white
            }

        /* HERO */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            padding-top: 80px
        }

        .hero-text {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 6rem 4rem 6rem 6rem
        }

        .hero-tag {
            font-size: .72rem;
            letter-spacing: .2em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--gold);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
            font-size: clamp(3rem,5vw,5rem);
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1.1;
            color: var(--brown);
            margin-bottom: 2rem
        }

            .hero-title em {
                font-style: italic;
                color: var(--red)
            }

        .hero-desc {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 420px;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 300
        }

        .hero-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            align-items: center
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--red);
            color: white;
            padding: .9rem 2.2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: .78rem;
            letter-spacing: .12em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: background .25s;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Jost',sans-serif
        }

            .btn-primary:hover {
                background: var(--brown)
            }

        .btn-secondary {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: .78rem;
            letter-spacing: .1em;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .5rem;
            transition: color .2s
        }

            .btn-secondary:hover {
                color: var(--gold)
            }

        .hero-image {
            background: var(--cream);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden
        }

        .hero-image-inner {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: #E8E0D0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden
        }

        .hero-photo {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform .6s ease
        }

            .hero-photo:hover {
                transform: scale(1.03)
            }

        .hero-badge {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 3rem;
            left: -1.5rem;
            background: var(--brown);
            color: var(--cream);
            padding: 1.2rem 2rem;
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
            font-size: .9rem;
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: .05em;
            box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 rgba(184,134,11,.3)
        }


        /* ABOUT */
        .about-strip {
            background: var(--brown);
            color: var(--cream);
            padding: 4rem 6rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 3rem;
            align-items: start
        }

        .about-stat {
            text-align: center
        }

        .about-stat-num {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--gold-light);
            display: block;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: .4rem
        }

        .about-stat-label {
            font-size: .75rem;
            letter-spacing: .15em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: rgba(245,240,232,.6)
        }

        /* MENU */
        .section {
            padding: 6rem
        }

        .section-header {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 4rem
        }

        .section-header-line {
            height: 1px;
            background: rgba(184,134,11,.3)
        }

        .section-header-center {
            text-align: center
        }

        .section-tag {
            font-size: .7rem;
            letter-spacing: .2em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--gold);
            margin-bottom: .5rem
        }

        .section-title {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
            font-size: 2.6rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--brown);
            line-height: 1.2
        }

        .menu-tabs {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(184,134,11,.2);
            flex-wrap: wrap
        }

        .menu-tab {
            padding: .7rem 2rem;
            font-size: .75rem;
            letter-spacing: .12em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border: none;
            background: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
            margin-bottom: -1px;
            transition: all .2s;
            font-family: 'Jost',sans-serif
        }

            .menu-tab.active {
                color: var(--red);
                border-bottom-color: var(--red)
            }

            .menu-tab:hover {
                color: var(--brown)
            }

        .menu-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr
        }

        .menu-item {
            padding: 1.4rem 2rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(184,134,11,.12);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: start;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            transition: background .2s
        }

            .menu-item:hover {
                background: rgba(245,240,232,.6)
            }

        .menu-item-info {
            flex: 1
        }

        .menu-item-name {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--brown);
            margin-bottom: .25rem
        }

        .menu-item-desc {
            font-size: .8rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-weight: 300
        }

        .menu-item-price {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--gold);
            font-weight: 600;
            white-space: nowrap;
            padding-top: .1rem
        }

        .menu-category {
            display: none
        }

            .menu-category.active {
                display: contents
            }

        /* SIGNATURE */
        .signature {
            background: var(--cream);
            padding: 6rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 5rem;
            align-items: center
        }

        .signature-visual {
            background: var(--warm-white);
            aspect-ratio: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative
        }

            .signature-visual::before {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                inset: 1.5rem;
                border: 1px solid rgba(184,134,11,.25)
            }

        .signature-tag {
            font-size: .7rem;
            letter-spacing: .2em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--gold);
            margin-bottom: 1rem
        }

        .signature-title {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--brown);
            line-height: 1.15;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem
        }

        .signature-desc {
            font-size: .95rem;
            line-height: 1.85;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-weight: 300
        }

        .ingredients {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 2rem
        }

        .ingredient-tag {
            font-size: .7rem;
            letter-spacing: .1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--brown-mid);
            border: 1px solid rgba(107,66,38,.3);
            padding: .35rem .9rem
        }

        /* TESTIMONIALS */
        .testimonials {
            padding: 6rem;
            background: var(--warm-white);
            text-align: center
        }

        .quotes-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem
        }

        .quote-card {
            background: var(--cream);
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            position: relative;
            text-align: left
        }

        .quote-mark {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
            font-size: 5rem;
            line-height: 1;
            color: rgba(184,134,11,.2);
            position: absolute;
            top: .5rem;
            left: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 300
        }

        .quote-text {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: 300;
            line-height: 1.75;
            color: var(--brown);
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem
        }

        .quote-author {
            font-size: .72rem;
            letter-spacing: .12em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--gold)
        }

        .stars {
            display: flex;
            gap: 3px;
            margin-bottom: .5rem
        }

        .star {
            color: var(--gold-light);
            font-size: .9rem
        }

        /* RESERVATION */
        .reservation {
            background: var(--brown);
            padding: 7rem 6rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 6rem;
            align-items: center;
            color: var(--cream)
        }

        .reservation-title {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--cream);
            line-height: 1.15;
            margin-bottom: 1rem
        }

        .reservation-desc {
            font-size: .9rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: rgba(245,240,232,.65);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-weight: 300
        }

        .info-block {
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem
        }

        .info-label {
            font-size: .65rem;
            letter-spacing: .18em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--gold-light);
            margin-bottom: .25rem
        }

        .info-value {
            font-size: .95rem;
            color: var(--cream);
            font-weight: 300
        }

        .res-form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem
        }

        .form-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1rem
        }

        .form-field {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: .4rem
        }

        .form-label {
            font-size: .65rem;
            letter-spacing: .15em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: rgba(245,240,232,.55)
        }

        .form-input, .form-select {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.07);
            border: 1px solid rgba(184,134,11,.3);
            color: var(--cream);
            padding: .75rem 1rem;
            font-family: 'Jost',sans-serif;
            font-size: .9rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            outline: none;
            transition: border-color .2s;
            appearance: none
        }

            .form-input::placeholder {
                color: rgba(245,240,232,.3)
            }

            .form-input:focus, .form-select:focus {
                border-color: var(--gold-light)
            }

            .form-select option {
                background: var(--brown)
            }

        .btn-reserve {
            margin-top: .5rem;
            background: var(--gold);
            color: var(--brown);
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border: none;
            font-family: 'Jost',sans-serif;
            font-size: .78rem;
            letter-spacing: .15em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: background .25s
        }

            .btn-reserve:hover {
                background: var(--gold-light)
            }

        /* FOOTER */
        footer {
            background: #1A1208;
            color: rgba(245,240,232,.5);
            padding: 3rem 6rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 3rem
        }

        .footer-brand {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--cream);
            margin-bottom: .8rem
        }

            .footer-brand span {
                color: var(--gold)
            }

        .footer-tagline {
            font-size: .8rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: rgba(245,240,232,.4);
            font-weight: 300;
            max-width: 220px
        }

        .footer-heading {
            font-size: .65rem;
            letter-spacing: .18em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--gold-light);
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem
        }

        .footer-links {
            list-style: none
        }

            .footer-links li {
                margin-bottom: .6rem
            }

            .footer-links a {
                text-decoration: none;
                font-size: .82rem;
                color: rgba(245,240,232,.45);
                transition: color .2s;
                font-weight: 300
            }

                .footer-links a:hover {
                    color: var(--gold-light)
                }

        .footer-bottom {
            background: #110D05;
            padding: 1.2rem 6rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: .72rem;
            color: rgba(245,240,232,.25)
        }

        /* TOAST */
        .toast {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 2rem;
            right: 2rem;
            background: var(--brown);
            color: var(--cream);
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            font-size: .85rem;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
            transform: translateX(130%);
            transition: transform .4s ease;
            z-index: 9999
        }

            .toast.show {
                transform: translateX(0)
            }

        /* MODAL */
        #loginModal {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            z-index: 9000;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0);
            display: none;
        }

            #loginModal.open {
                display: flex;
                background: rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
                backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
                -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
            }

        .modal-box {
            background: #FAF7F2;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 440px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 2.8rem 3rem 2.4rem;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 24px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.3);
            transform: translateY(-24px);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: transform .3s ease, opacity .3s ease;
        }

        #loginModal.open .modal-box {
            transform: translateY(0);
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .modal-close-btn {
            position: absolute;
            top: .9rem;
            right: 1rem;
            width: 2rem;
            height: 2rem;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1;
            color: #7A6558;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: color .2s;
        }

            .modal-close-btn:hover {
                color: #3D2B1F
            }

        .modal-heading {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: #3D2B1F;
            margin-bottom: .35rem;
        }

        .modal-sub {
            font-size: .88rem;
            color: #7A6558;
            margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .mf {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: .35rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem
        }

        .ml {
            font-size: .65rem;
            letter-spacing: .15em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #7A6558
        }

        .mi {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid rgba(184,134,11,.28);
            color: #2A1F17;
            padding: .75rem 1rem;
            font-family: 'Jost',sans-serif;
            font-size: .92rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            outline: none;
            border-radius: 2px;
            transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s;
            width: 100%;
        }

            .mi:focus {
                border-color: #B8860B;
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(184,134,11,.12)
            }

            .mi::placeholder {
                color: rgba(42,31,23,.3)
            }

        .modal-error {
            font-size: .8rem;
            color: #8B1A1A;
            min-height: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: .5rem;
            display: none;
        }

            .modal-error.visible {
                display: block
            }

        .modal-submit {
            width: 100%;
            background: #8B1A1A;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 1rem;
            font-family: 'Jost',sans-serif;
            font-size: .78rem;
            letter-spacing: .15em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: background .25s;
            margin-top: .25rem;
        }

            .modal-submit:hover {
                background: #3D2B1F
            }

            .modal-submit:disabled {
                background: #bbb;
                cursor: not-allowed
            }

        .modal-footer {
            margin-top: 1.1rem;
            font-size: .8rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: #7A6558
        }

            .modal-footer a {
                color: #B8860B;
                text-decoration: none
            }

                .modal-footer a:hover {
                    text-decoration: underline
                }

        .modal-divider {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .8rem;
            margin: 1.2rem 0
        }

            .modal-divider::before, .modal-divider::after {
                content: '';
                flex: 1;
                height: 1px;
                background: rgba(184,134,11,.2)
            }

            .modal-divider span {
                font-size: .68rem;
                letter-spacing: .1em;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                color: #7A6558
            }

        body.no-scroll {
            overflow: hidden
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- NAV -->
    <nav>
        <div class="nav-logo">Trattoria <span>Bella</span></div>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="#menu">Menu</a></li>
            <li><a href="#about">Our Story</a></li>
            <li><a href="#reservation">Reserve</a></li>
        </ul>
        <button class="nav-login" id="openLoginBtn">Login</button>
    </nav>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <p class="hero-tag">Since 1987 · Florence, Tuscany</p>
            <h1 class="hero-title">Where Italy<br>finds its<br><em>truest voice</em></h1>
            <p class="hero-desc">Hand-rolled pasta, wood-fired meats, and recipes carried across generations. Every dish is a letter from home.</p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
                <a href="#menu" class="btn-primary">Explore Menu</a>
                <a href="#reservation" class="btn-secondary">Reserve a Table →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-image">
            <div class="hero-image-inner">
                <img class="hero-photo" src="img/grandmas-lasagna-hero-02-FT-RECIPE1222-e0117c061ce74af8b2dfae19d08c91a5.webp" alt="Grandma's lasagna">
            </div>
            <div class="hero-badge">La nostra passione è la cucina</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- STATS -->
    <div class="about-strip" id="about">
        <div class="about-stat"><span class="about-stat-num">37</span><span class="about-stat-label">Years of Tradition</span></div>
        <div class="about-stat"><span class="about-stat-num">12</span><span class="about-stat-label">Seasonal Ingredients</span></div>
        <div class="about-stat"><span class="about-stat-num">3</span><span class="about-stat-label">Generations of Family Recipes</span></div>
    </div>

    <!-- MENU -->
    <section class="section" id="menu">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-header-line"></div>
            <div class="section-header-center">
                <p class="section-tag">Il Nostro Menu</p>
                <h2 class="section-title">A Symphony of Flavours</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="section-header-line"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-tabs">
            <button class="menu-tab active" data-tab="antipasti">Appetizers</button>
            <button class="menu-tab" data-tab="primi">First Courses</button>
            <button class="menu-tab" data-tab="secondi">Second Courses</button>
            <button class="menu-tab" data-tab="dolci">Desserts</button>
            <button class="menu-tab" data-tab="wine">Wine & Drinks</button>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-grid">
